<!-- pages/task-create/task-create.wxml —— 新建排班任务（对齐逻辑链：mode + 基础模板 + 日期 + 约束） -->
<view class="page-tc">
  <view class="tc-hero">
    <view class="hero-icon">＋</view>
    <view class="hero-body">
      <view class="hero-title">新建排班任务</view>
      <view class="hero-desc">选模式与作息模板 → 定日期 → 发布收集</view>
    </view>
    <view class="hero-group">
      <text class="hg-label">所属分组</text>
      <text class="hg-name">{{groupName}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="stepper">
    <view wx:for="{{steps}}" wx:key="key" class="step {{step >= index + 1 ? 'step-done' : ''}} {{step === index + 1 ? 'step-current' : ''}}">
      <view class="step-num">{{index + 1}}</view>
      <view class="step-label">{{item.label}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 1 基础 -->
  <view class="section-card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="sh-num">1</view>
      <view class="sh-title">基础信息</view>
      <view class="sh-optional">必填</view>
    </view>
    <view class="section-body">
      <view class="field">
        <view class="field-label">任务标题 <text class="req">*</text></view>
        <input class="input" placeholder="如：国庆假期值班" value="{{title}}" bindinput="onTitleInput" maxlength="30" />
        <view class="field-hint">{{title.length}}/30 字</view>
      </view>
      <view class="field">
        <view class="field-label">任务描述 <text class="opt">选填</text></view>
        <textarea class="textarea" placeholder="补充说明，如值班地点、注意事项等" value="{{description}}" bindinput="onDescInput" maxlength="200" />
        <view class="field-hint">{{description.length}}/200 字</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 2 日期 -->
  <view class="section-card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="sh-num">2</view>
      <view class="sh-title">日期范围</view>
    </view>
    <view class="section-body">
      <view class="field-row">
        <view class="field-cell">
          <view class="field-label">开始日期</view>
          <picker mode="date" value="{{dateStart}}" bindchange="onDateStart">
            <view class="picker-value">{{dateStart || '请选择'}}</view>
          </picker>
        </view>
        <view class="field-cell">
          <view class="field-label">结束日期</view>
          <picker mode="date" value="{{dateEnd}}" bindchange="onDateEnd">
            <view class="picker-value">{{dateEnd || '请选择'}}</view>
          </picker>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="field">
        <view class="field-label">循环规则</view>
        <view class="cycle-row">
          <view
            wx:for="{{cycleRules}}"
            wx:key="key"
            class="cycle-chip {{cycleRule === item.key ? 'cycle-active' : ''}}"
            bindtap="pickCycle"
            data-key="{{item.key}}"
          >{{item.label}}</view>
        </view>
        <view wx:if="{{cycleRule === 'custom'}}" class="custom-cycle">
          <view class="cc-title">选择循环周次</view>
          <view class="cc-weeks">
            <view
              wx:for="{{allWeeks}}"
              wx:key="value"
              class="cc-week {{customWeeks[item.value] ? 'cc-week-active' : ''}}"
              bindtap="toggleCustomWeek"
              data-value="{{item.value}}"
            >{{item.label}}</view>
          </view>
          <view wx:if="{{customWeeksLabel}}" class="cc-summary">已选：{{customWeeksLabel}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 3 时段：mode + 基础模板（逻辑链核心） -->
  <view class="section-card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="sh-num">3</view>
      <view class="sh-title">时段配置</view>
      <view wx:if="{{allowEditRanges}}" class="sh-action" bindtap="addPeriod">＋ 添加</view>
    </view>
    <view class="section-body">
      <view class="period-tip">
        <view class="tip-icon">ⓘ</view>
        <text>先选展示方式，再选基础作息模板（众数种子，可改）。任务将保存时段快照，改模板不影响历史任务。</text>
      </view>

      <view class="field">
        <view class="field-label">展示方式</view>
        <picker mode="selector" range="{{modeOptions}}" range-key="name" value="{{modeIndex}}" bindchange="onModeChange">
          <view class="picker-value picker-block">{{timeModeLabel}} · {{modeOptions[modeIndex].desc}}</view>
        </picker>
      </view>

      <view class="field">
        <view class="field-label">基础作息模板</view>
        <picker mode="selector" range="{{profileOptions}}" range-key="name" value="{{profileIndex}}" bindchange="onProfileChange">
          <view class="picker-value picker-block">
            {{profileOptions[profileIndex].name || '加载模板…'}}
            <text wx:if="{{profileOptions[profileIndex]}}">（{{periods.length}} 段）</text>
          </view>
        </picker>
        <view class="field-hint" wx:if="{{profileOptions[profileIndex].description}}">{{profileOptions[profileIndex].description}}</view>
      </view>

      <!-- 预览：按 mode 显示节次名 / 时间 -->
      <scroll-view scroll-x class="period-preview-scroll" enable-flex>
        <view class="period-chip-preview" wx:for="{{periods}}" wx:key="id">
          <view class="pcp-name" wx:if="{{showSectionName}}">{{item.name}}</view>
          <view class="pcp-time" wx:if="{{showTimeRange && item.start}}">{{item.start}}-{{item.end}}</view>
          <view class="pcp-name" wx:if="{{!showSectionName && !showTimeRange}}">{{item.label || item.name}}</view>
        </view>
      </scroll-view>

      <!-- range 模式可微调起止 -->
      <block wx:if="{{allowEditRanges}}">
        <view wx:for="{{periods}}" wx:key="id" class="period-row">
          <view class="period-row-head">
            <text class="period-row-label">时段 {{index + 1}}</text>
            <view wx:if="{{periods.length > 1}}" class="period-row-del" bindtap="delPeriod" data-index="{{index}}">删除</view>
          </view>
          <view class="period-row-body">
            <picker mode="time" value="{{item.start}}" bindchange="onPeriodStart" data-index="{{index}}">
              <view class="time-picker">{{item.start}}</view>
            </picker>
            <text class="time-sep">—</text>
            <picker mode="time" value="{{item.end}}" bindchange="onPeriodEnd" data-index="{{index}}">
              <view class="time-picker">{{item.end}}</view>
            </picker>
            <view class="period-preview period-chip period-chip-active">{{item.start}}-{{item.end}}</view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </block>

      <view wx:else class="period-readonly-hint">
        节次类模板由基础作息生成；如需自由改钟点，请切换为「按时间段」。
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 4 约束 -->
  <view class="section-card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="sh-num">4</view>
      <view class="sh-title">约束与截止</view>
    </view>
    <view class="section-body">
      <view class="field">
        <view class="field-label">每时段最少人数</view>
        <view class="counter">
          <view class="counter-btn" bindtap="decMinPeople">−</view>
          <view class="counter-value">{{minPeople}}</view>
          <view class="counter-btn counter-btn-plus" bindtap="incMinPeople">＋</view>
          <view class="counter-unit">人 / 时段</view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="field">
        <view class="field-label">每人每周最大次数 <text class="opt">选填</text></view>
        <view class="counter">
          <view class="counter-btn {{maxPerWeek === null ? 'disabled' : ''}}" bindtap="decMaxWeek">−</view>
          <view class="counter-value">{{maxPerWeek === null ? '不限' : maxPerWeek}}</view>
          <view class="counter-btn counter-btn-plus {{maxPerWeek === null ? 'disabled' : ''}}" bindtap="incMaxWeek">＋</view>
          <view class="counter-unit">次 / 周</view>
          <view class="counter-clear" bindtap="clearMaxWeek">{{maxPerWeek === null ? '设置' : '不限'}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="field">
        <view class="field-label">截止时间 <text class="req">*</text></view>
        <view class="deadline-chips">
          <view
            wx:for="{{deadlineOptions}}"
            wx:key="key"
            class="dl-chip {{deadlineType === item.key ? 'dl-active' : ''}}"
            bindtap="pickDeadline"
            data-key="{{item.key}}"
          >{{item.label}}</view>
        </view>
        <picker wx:if="{{deadlineType === 'custom'}}" mode="date" value="{{deadlineDate}}" bindchange="onDeadlineDate">
          <view class="picker-value picker-block">{{deadlineDate || '请选择截止日期'}}</view>
        </picker>
        <picker wx:if="{{deadlineType === 'custom'}}" mode="time" value="{{deadlineTime}}" bindchange="onDeadlineTime">
          <view class="picker-value picker-block">{{deadlineTime || '请选择截止时间'}}</view>
        </picker>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 摘要 -->
  <view class="summary-card">
    <view class="sc-title">任务摘要</view>
    <view class="sc-row">
      <text class="sc-label">分组</text>
      <text class="sc-value">{{groupName}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="sc-row">
      <text class="sc-label">模式</text>
      <text class="sc-value">{{timeModeLabel}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="sc-row">
      <text class="sc-label">日期</text>
      <text class="sc-value">{{dateStart}} — {{dateEnd}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="sc-row">
      <text class="sc-label">时段</text>
      <text class="sc-value">{{periods.length}} 个 · {{periodsSummary}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="sc-row">
      <text class="sc-label">约束</text>
      <text class="sc-value">每时段 ≥ {{minPeople}} 人{{maxPerWeek !== null ? ' · 每周 ≤ ' + maxPerWeek + ' 次' : ''}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="sc-row">
      <text class="sc-label">截止</text>
      <text class="sc-value">{{deadlineLabel}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="bottom-bar">
    <view class="btn btn-outline" bindtap="saveDraft">保存草稿</view>
    <view class="btn btn-primary btn-block {{submitting ? 'btn-disabled' : ''}}" bindtap="onPublish">
      {{submitting ? '提交中…' : '立即发布'}}
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
